Linux 16.04
sudo apt-get install build-essential
sudo apt-get install cmake git libgtk2.0-dev pkg-config libavcodec-dev libavformat-dev libswscale-dev
clone your fork repository from opencv
cd your opencv repository
cmake -DETHASHCL=ON -DETHASHCUDA=ON -DAPICORE=ON -H. -Bbuild
When done you will get this feedback
-- Configuring done
-- Generating done
-- Build files have been written to: /home/../opencv/build
